    <p>Buyers reach this page from every phrasing — macaw parrot vs African grey, African grey parrot vs macaw, even "african gray" with an <em>a</em> — and a fair number arrive already comparing all three big parrot camps at once, African Grey vs Macaw vs Cockatoo. We raise Greys, so we'll name that bias up front: everything below is still the honest version, including every place a macaw genuinely wins. The rest of this page settles which bird fits your specific household, species by species.</p>
